{"word":"H2372 - חָזָה - châzâh - khaw-zaw' - Behold","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָזָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>châzâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khaw-zaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Behold"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - காண், தரிசி, பார், நோக்கு, பார்க்கப்படு, திருஷ்டி, இதோ, தரிசனஞ்சொல், ஏற்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to see, to perceive, to look, to behold, to prophesy, to provide (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to see, to behold"},{"paragraph":"2) to see as a seer in the ecstatic state"},{"paragraph":"3) to see, to perceive"},{"paragraph":"a) with the intelligence"},{"paragraph":"b) to see (by experience)"},{"paragraph":"c) to provide"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>gaze</i> at; mentally to <i>perceive</i>, <i>contemplate</i> (with pleasure); specifically to <i>have a vision of: - </i>behold, look, prophesy, provide, see."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2335 - חֹוזַי - Chôwzay - kho-zah'-ee/2335\">H2335</a>, <a href=\"#/H2371 - חֲזָאֵל - Chăzâʼêl - khaz-aw-ale'/2371\">H2371</a>, <a href=\"#/H2372 - חָזָה - châzâh - khaw-zaw'/2372\">H2372</a>, <a href=\"#/H2374 - חֹזֶה - chôzeh - kho-zeh'/2374\">H2374</a>, <a href=\"#/H2377 - חָזֹון - châzôwn - khaw-zone'/2377\">H2377</a>, <a href=\"#/H2378 - חָזֹות - châzôwth - khaw-zooth'/2378\">H2378</a>, <a href=\"#/H2380 - חָזוּת - châzûwth - khaw-zooth'/2380\">H2380</a>, <a href=\"#/H2381 - חֲזִיאֵל - Chăzîyʼêl - khaz-ee-ale'/2381\">H2381</a>, <a href=\"#/H2382 - חֲזָיָה - Chăzâyâh - khaz-aw-yaw'/2382\">H2382</a>, <a href=\"#/H2383 - חֶזְיֹון - Chezyôwn - khez-yone'/2383\">H2383</a>, <a href=\"#/H2384 - חִזָּיֹון - chizzâyôwn - khiz-zaw-yone'/2384\">H2384</a>, <a href=\"#/H3166 - יַחֲזִיאֵל - Yachăzîyʼêl - yakh-az-ee-ale'/3166\">H3166</a>, <a href=\"#/H3167 - יַחְזְיָה - Yachzᵉyâh - yakh-zeh-yaw'/3167\">H3167</a>, <a href=\"#/H4236 - מַחֲזֶה - machăzeh - makh-az-eh'/4236\">H4236</a>, <a href=\"#/H4237 - מֶחֱזָה - mechĕzâh - mekh-ez-aw'/4237\">H4237</a>, <a href=\"#/H4238 - מַחֲזִיאֹות - Machăzîyʼôwth - makh-az-ee-oth'/4238\">H4238</a>"}]}